{"tid":2204491,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"踢開對岸華衣《逆統戰》揭示真實一面","createTime":"2020-09-16T05:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T12:06:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c80bedbb0e4dcb6ba3919bee4e6bb448518fb573","tid":2204491,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200916/U6CVBGAUKJEY5L4X4XWTQSCLRY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200916%2FU6CVBGAUKJEY5L4X4XWTQSCLRY%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=6a4001b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200916%2FU6CVBGAUKJEY5L4X4XWTQSCLRY%2F&h=7e62f62b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200916/U6CVBGAUKJEY5L4X4XWTQSCLRY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n踢開對岸華衣《逆統戰》揭示真實一面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tw3MmXc8taz_xOGBym_4tTEU0Z8=/1544x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/REQPH3AFT5BCJCUC57K7KVXC3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ftw3MmXc8taz_xOGBym_4tTEU0Z8%3D%2F1544x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FREQPH3AFT5BCJCUC57K7KVXC3M.jpg&h=8b7cca3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■抗爭者以黑衣造型，代表香港的部份。<br />\n<br />\n「長年生長於憂患意識，大眾的心理已經從幾年前比較幼稚的失敗主義中逐漸走出，心理上變得比較自信、勇敢。過去那種國際孤兒的自卑感已經逐漸散去。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：遊戲轉化現實 需觸動玩家<br />\n<br />\n桌上遊戲《逆統戰》背景是現實，也是架空的世界。內容是各個少數民族、香港、台灣甚至清朝（滿洲），如何與中共周旋的遊戲。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n開發團隊50人， 年齡從20歲到50歲，早前眾籌，短短三周已經籌達近159萬港元，計劃也會推出電子遊戲，「因為我們的支持者和贊助人已經遠遠超出了較關心政治議題的族群，這是很值得欣慰的。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：紅色資本滲透 開發《赤毒》警醒玩家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/I2iltisPar1AXr2fiE1BquLRZqk=/1570x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H7QXZWZH6VHMFEYFAFZ6F4EC5A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FI2iltisPar1AXr2fiE1BquLRZqk%3D%2F1570x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH7QXZWZH6VHMFEYFAFZ6F4EC5A.jpg&h=a4a2629d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■桌遊《逆統戰》的故事，圍繞着台灣、滿洲、香港、蒙古、哈薩克、維吾爾及藏國，如何抵抗紅軍為中心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NjDWVN-BgIM3OvLoHl_Z1_ZyIUE=/1050x468/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T6ZTQG67Y5FMFNXE3QSCOCAUV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNjDWVN-BgIM3OvLoHl_Z1_ZyIUE%3D%2F1050x468%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT6ZTQG67Y5FMFNXE3QSCOCAUV4.jpg&h=bb902485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■開發團隊於三周內眾籌達159萬港元，更計劃推出電子遊戲，可見支持者眾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盼由認識帶出正確判斷<br />\n<br />\n台灣一直不被國際看見，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n八、九十後的台灣年輕人，生長於被對岸導彈瞄準的陰影下，「無力感可能在上一個世代會比較嚴重，90、00以後的世代可說是已經習慣這種陰影了。」近年與香港連成一線，在國際上也讓世界看見，台灣好像也能鑽到自己的定位，重建台灣人的自信心，「新一代的台灣人目睹了中共在香港的暴行，更加激發了台灣人對中共的痛恨，不再相信中共的言辭。」<br />\n<br />\n遊戲不只是遊戲，《逆統戰》的野心或許比大眾理解的「遊戲」還要深重，「。。。。。。。。。。。。。。這樣台灣人才能對中國的綜合國力產生正確的認識，正確的認識才能帶來正確的判斷。」"},{"pid":"b96a528096525dbdebd603606145f505171040b3","tid":2204491,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:02:14.000Z","msg":"開發團隊50人咁多？"},{"pid":"26b37613e1493033e37bccfbc7f13c43bc2c1944","tid":2204491,"uid":71199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"好想買盒同friend 玩"},{"pid":"41eb766a5e9e53416f87e8b0b8555fcb43123e4d","tid":2204491,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c80bedbb0e4dcb6ba3919bee4e6bb448518fb573","tid":2204491,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200916/U6CVBGAUKJEY5L4X4XWTQSCLRY/\" data-sr-url=